{
  "execution": "single",
  "pageHead": {
    "title": "Metrobank's Spark Joy Promo"
  },
  "pages": {
    "home": {
      "template": "home-main",
      "sections": [
        {
          "id": "cover",
          "component": "cover-image",
          "props": {
            "coverUrl": "https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/assets.giftaway.ph/images/affiliates/mcc-universalsite/metrobank-generic-banner.webp"
          },
          "classes": {
            "outer": "-mx-6"
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "heading",
          "component": "heading-hero",
          "props": {
            "title": "Join the Metrobank Spark Joy Promo",
            "description": "Take the first step to sparking joy with Metrobank! Simply save more and get rewarded with an eGift of up to PHP 10,000."
          },
          "classes": {
            "outer": "text-start"
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "campaign",
          "component": "accumulated-spend-multiple-by-tier",
          "props": {
            "rewards": [
              {
                "tier": 1,
                "title": "₱300 eGC",
                "description": "For ₱15K to <25K ADB"
              },
              {
                "tier": 2,
                "title": "₱500 eGC",
                "description": "For ₱25K to <50K ADB"
              },
              {
                "tier": 3,
                "title": "₱1,500 eGC",
                "description": "For ₱50K to <100K ADB"
              },
              {
                "tier": 4,
                "title": "₱2,000 eGC",
                "description": "For ₱100K to <500K ADB"
              },
              {
                "tier": 5,
                "title": "₱10,000 eGC",
                "description": "For ₱500K and up ADB"
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "how-this-works",
          "component": "sheet-markdown-content",
          "props": {
            "triggerText": "How this works",
            "triggerIcon": "lucide:message-circle-question",
            "sheetTitle": "How this works",
            "sheetContent": "$$**Save ₱15,000 or more** to earn **eGCs worth up to ₱10,000!** Simply maintain your deposit or continue saving for 6 months to boost your reward!\n\n| Average Daily Balance | eGC Reward        |\n|-----------------------|-------------------|\n| ₱15K to <₱25K         | ₱300 eGC          |\n| ₱25K to <₱50K         | ₱500 eGC          |\n| ₱50K to <₱100K        | ₱1,500 eGC        |\n| ₱100K to <₱500K       | ₱2,000 eGC        |\n| ₱500K and up         | ₱10,000 eGC     |"
          },
          "classes": {
            "trigger": "mt-6"
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "footer",
          "component": "footer-legal-clause",
          "props": {
            "affiliate": "Metrobank"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    "login": {
      "template": "login-with-otp",
      "states": ["login", "otp", "success", "expired"],
      "sections": [
        {
          "id": "cover",
          "component": "cover-image",
          "props": {
            "coverUrl": "https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/assets.giftaway.ph/images/affiliates/mcc-universalsite/metrobank-generic-banner.webp"
          },
          "classes": {
            "outer": "-mx-6"
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "heading",
          "component": "heading-hero",
          "props": {
            "title": "Join the Metrobank Spark Joy Promo",
            "description": "Take the first step to sparking joy with Metrobank! Simply save more and get rewarded with an eGift of up to PHP 10,000."
          },
          "classes": {
            "outer": "text-start"
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "form-login",
          "component": "form-login",
          "state": "login",
          "alert": {
            "component": "alert-card",
            "map": {
              "InvalidUserPassword": {
                "type": "error",
                "title": "Invalid Mobile Number",
                "description": "The mobile number is either invalid or not yet registered for this promotion."
              }
            }
          },
          "schema": [
            {
              "$el": "h1",
              "children": "Login",
              "attrs": {
                "class": "text-2xl font-bold mb-8"
              }
            },
            {
              "$formkit": "tel",
              "name": "mobileno",
              "id": "mobileno",
              "label": "Mobile Number",
              "validation": [["required"], ["matches", "/^(09)[0-9]{9}$/"]],
              "placeholder": "09XX-XXX-XXXX",
              "validationMessages": {
                "matches": "Please enter your 11-digit Philippine mobile number."
              }
            },
            {
              "$formkit": "checkbox",
              "name": "terms",
              "id": "terms",
              "label": "This promo treats website is managed by Giftaway. By logging in, the information you provide on the site will be subject to the Terms of Service of Giftaway.",
              "validation": [["accepted"]],
              "validationLabel": "Terms and Conditions",
              "validationMessages": {
                "accepted": "Agreeing to the terms and condition is required."
              },
              "decorator-icon": "check",
              "classes": {
                "wrapper": "flex gap-x-1 items-start",
                "label": "text-xs text-neutral-500 leading-6 text-pretty",
                "inner": "mt-1 shrink-0",
                "decorator": "rounded-xs h-[20px] w-[20px]"
              },
              "sectionsSchema": {
                "label": {
                  "children": [
                    "This promo treats website is managed by Giftaway. By logging in, the information you provide on the site will be subject to the ",
                    {
                      "$el": "a",
                      "attrs": {
                        "href": "https://giftaway.ph/terms",
                        "target": "_blank",
                        "class": "underline text-primary"
                      },
                      "children": "Terms of Service"
                    },
                    " of Giftaway."
                  ]
                }
              }
            },
            {
              "$formkit": "submit",
              "type": "submit",
              "id": "submit",
              "name": "submit",
              "label": "Login",
              "disabled": "$isPending || $state.valid === false",
              "children": {
                "if": "$isPending && $state.valid",
                "then": {
                  "$el": "span",
                  "attrs": {
                    "class": "w-6 h-6 border-2 border-surface-1 border-r-transparent mr-2 rounded-full animate-spin"
                  }
                },
                "else": "$label"
              }
            },
            {
              "$el": "p",
              "attrs": {
                "class": "text-sm text-center text-text-secondary mt-4 text-pretty"
              },
              "children": [
                "Don't have an account yet? ",
                {
                  "$cmp": "NuxtLink",
                  "props": {
                    "to": "register",
                    "class": "text-primary font-semibold"
                  },
                  "children": "Register here"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "form-login-otp",
          "component": "form-login-otp",
          "state": "otp",
          "schema": [
            {
              "$el": "h1",
              "children": "Verification",
              "attrs": {
                "class": "text-2xl font-bold mb-8"
              }
            },
            {
              "$formkit": "text",
              "name": "code",
              "id": "code",
              "label": "Enter Verification Code",
              "validation": "required|length:6,6",
              "validationMessages": {
                "length": "Verification code must be 6 digits."
              },
              "validationLabel": "Verification Code",
              "placeholder": "XXXXXX",
              "help": "We sent a 6-digit verification code to your mobile number.",
              "attrs": {
                "inputmode": "numeric",
                "autocomplete": "one-time-code"
              },
              "classes": {
                "help": "text-neutral-500 text-pretty"
              },
              "sectionsSchema": {
                "help": {
                  "children": "$: 'We sent a 6-digit verification code to your mobile number ending in ' + $formkitSlice($mobileno, -4) + '.'"
                }
              }
            },
            {
              "$formkit": "submit",
              "type": "submit",
              "id": "submit",
              "name": "submit",
              "label": "Proceed",
              "disabled": "$isPending || $state.valid === false",
              "children": {
                "if": "$isPending && $state.valid",
                "then": {
                  "$el": "span",
                  "attrs": {
                    "class": "w-6 h-6 border-2 border-surface-1 border-r-transparent mr-2 rounded-full animate-spin"
                  }
                },
                "else": "$label"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "how-this-works",
          "component": "sheet-markdown-content",
          "props": {
            "triggerText": "How this works",
            "triggerIcon": "lucide:message-circle-question",
            "sheetTitle": "How this works",
            "sheetContent": "$$**Save ₱15,000 or more** to earn **eGCs worth up to ₱10,000!** Simply maintain your deposit or continue saving for 6 months to boost your reward!\n\n| Average Daily Balance | eGC Reward        |\n|-----------------------|-------------------|\n| ₱15K to <₱25K         | ₱300 eGC          |\n| ₱25K to <₱50K         | ₱500 eGC          |\n| ₱50K to <₱100K        | ₱1,500 eGC        |\n| ₱100K to <₱500K       | ₱2,000 eGC        |\n| ₱500K and up         | ₱10,000 eGC     |"
          },
          "classes": {
            "trigger": "mt-6"
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "footer",
          "component": "footer-legal-clause",
          "props": {
            "affiliate": "Metrobank"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
